INSTALLING SEDNACOM EXTRAS
==========================

Zarafa side
===========

Install content of php subdirectory in the top-level directory of Zarafa web-access.

List of files: 
    appointment.php
    contact.php
    delete_appointment.php
    get_emails.php
    liste_email.php
    sednamail.php

OpenERP side
============

Install this directory as a regular OpenERP module.

Configure OpenERP users: in the "Zarafa" tab, fill up fields as following:
 - server : the url to reach zarafa web-access (eg http://zarafa.mycompany.com/webaccess)
 - login : zarafa login of the user
 - password : zarafa password of the user
 - email : email address of the user 

